data.description:
Türkiye’nin indirim ve lezzeti buluşturan yemek sipariş uygulaması Tıkla Gelsin® ile tanış!

Online yemek siparişlerinde en sevdiğin lezzetlere kolayca ulaşmak, kampanyalar ve indirim avantajlarından faydalanmak istiyorsan adres belli. Tıkla Gelsin®, yemek yemek istediğin her an yanı başında. Kupon fırsatları ve Gel Al seçeneğiyle Tıkla Gelsin®, yemek siparişini hesaplı ve pratik hale getiriyor!

Neden Tıkla Gelsin®?
-Geniş restoran ağı: Türkiye'nin dört bir yanından binlerce restoran ve mutfak seçeneğine ulaş.
-Özel indirimler ve kampanyalar: Siparişlerinde indirimlerden faydalanma şansını yakala.
-Kolay ve hızlı sipariş: Kullanıcı dostu arayüz sayesinde siparişlerini birkaç dokunuşla tamamla.
-Canlı takip: Siparişinin tüm aşamalarını anlık takip et.
-Güvenli ödeme: Tıklapay Cüzdan, kredi kartı, banka kartı, yemek kartları ve diğer güvenli ödeme yöntemleri ile rahatça öde.
-Gel Al seçeneği: En sevdiğin lezzetleri sıra beklemeden ister restoranda ye ister paket olarak teslim al.
-Cüzdan özelliği: Tıklapay Cüzdan özelliği ile yaptığın yüklemelerde Tıkla Para kazan ve siparişlerinde kullan.
-Arkadaşını davet et: Arkadaşlarını Tıkla Gelsin® dünyasına davet ederek Tıkla Para’ları kap.
-Canlı destek: Chatbot 7/24 hizmetinde. Ayrıca 10:00-03:00 saatleri arasında canlı destek ekibimiz de yanında.

Yemek siparişi artık çok kolay
Online yemek dünyası ve sipariş uygulamalarının yıldızı Tıkla Gelsin®, her damak zevkine uygun geniş restoran ve mutfak seçenekleriyle burada! Döner siparişi, pizza siparişi, tavuk yemekleri, içecekler ve diğer enfes lezzetler… Evde, işte ya da restoranda canın ne çekiyorsa birkaç tık uzağında. Tıkla Gelsin® kupon, kampanya ve indirim fırsatlarıyla enfes lezzetlere indirimlerle ulaşmanın tadını çıkar!

Gününü güzelleştirecek tüm yiyecek ve içecekler sen neredeysen orada
Sana Gelsin ile favori restoranını seç, istediğin yemekleri sepete ekle, online ya da kapıda dilediğin gibi öde. Siparişin hızlıca elinde!

Tıklapay ile kolayca öde
-Tıklapay Cüzdan’ına hızlı ve güvenli bir şekilde para yükle, siparişlerinde pratik ödeme deneyimini yaşa.
-Tıklapay Cüzdan ile sevdiklerine anında para transferi yap, işlemlerini birkaç tıkla tamamla.

Sepette indirim fırsatlarını kaçırma
Tıkla Gelsin® yemek sitesi ve yemek siparişi uygulaması, kullanıcılarına benzersiz kampanyalar ve indirimler sunuyor. Burger King® siparişi, Popeyes® siparişi, Arby’s® siparişi, Subway® siparişi, Sbarro® siparişi, Usta Dönerci®, Usta Pideci® siparişi, Amasya Et Ürünleri® siparişi, Milgo® siparişi… Tıkla Gelsin® ile hepsi aynı uygulamada! Yapman gereken tek şey sepetini enfes lezzetlerle doldurmak ve indirim fırsatlarını yakalamak!

Oyna Kazan ile Eğlence Seni Bekliyor! 
Tıkla Gelsin®’in Oyna Kazan özelliğiyle şansını deneyerek sürpriz hediyeler kazanabilirsin.

Gel Al ile Sıra Bekleme!
Tıkla Gelsin® Gel Al ile sıra beklemeden siparişini verip yemeğini restoranda kolayca teslim alabilirsin.

Tıkla Gelsin® ile siparişin kapında
Online yemek siparişi vermenin en güzel yanı da seçtiğin lezzetlere ev konforunda ve kolayca ulaşabilmek. Tıkla Gelsin® uygulamasıyla dilediğin lezzetler kapına geliyor. Böylece favori yiyecek ve içeceklerine evinden çıkmadan ulaşmanın keyfini çıkarabilirsin.

Fırsatlar ve İndirimler Tıkla Gelsin®’de
Tıklapay Cüzdan özelliği, ilk yüklemeye özel yüklediğin miktara göre değişen oranda Tıkla Para kazandırıyor. Sonraki para yüklemelerinde kazancını çoğaltma şansın var! Üstelik Arkadaşını Davet Et özelliği de Tıkla Para kazanma fırsatı sunuyor.
Lezzetli yemeklerin keyfini çıkarmak hiç bu kadar kolay olmamıştı. Hemen Tıkla Gelsin®’i indir ve keyifli bir yemek deneyimi yaşa!

T.C. Sağlık Bakanlığı’nın sunduğu “Hastane Randevu Merkezi” mobil uygulaması, iPad’iniz ve iPhone’unuz için özel olarak tasarlanmış olup, hem uygulamanın kendisi hem de randevu almak ücretsizdir. Uygulamanın kısa adı “MHRS” dir.
 
MHRS Mobil ile tüm Türkiye’de Sağlık Bakanlığına bağlı Devlet Hastaneleri, Ağız ve Diş Sağlığı Hastaneleri ve Merkezleri (ADSH, ADSM) için vatandaşların, istedikleri hekimden ve belirledikleri uygun olan tarihe randevu almaları sağlanır.
 
Bundan böyle hastanelerde uzun sıralar beklemenize gerek yok. MHRS Mobil uygulaması yardımı ile kolay ve hızlıca muayene randevusu alabilir ve aldığınız randevuları buradan takip edebilirsiniz. Randevu gününü, saatini, ve hekiminizin o gün hastanede görev yapıp yapmadığını öğrenebilir, gidemeyeceğiniz randevularınızı buradan iptal edebilirsiniz.
 
Hastane Randevu Merkezine ulaşmak için ayrıca internet üzerinden www.hastanerandevu.gov.tr adresini kullanabilir ya da ALO 182 MHRS Çağrı Merkezini arayarak kendinize ve yakınlarınıza randevu alabilirsiniz.

data.description:
Met OVpay kun je in- en uitchecken met je betaalpas, creditcard of mobiel. Deze app hoort bij OVpay. Al eens met je (mobiele) betaalpas gereisd, of ben je dit van plan? Dan is deze app echt iets voor jou.
 
Dit kun je allemaal in de app:
 
• Bekijk of je in- of uitgecheckt bent
Nooit meer onzeker of je wel of niet bent in-of uitgecheckt. Dit zie je bij je Reizen. Of zet een melding aan. Dan krijg je een melding op je mobiel zodra je bent in- of uitgecheckt.
 
• Pas je in- of uitcheck aan
Ben je toch een keer vergeten om in of uit te checken? Of is dit niet goed gegaan? Je past dit aan in de app. Dit kun je nog doen tot wel 60 dagen terug.
 
• Al je ritten en reiskosten in één overzicht
Onder het kopje Reizen vind je al je ritten. Je kunt terugkijken tot 18 maanden.
 
• Maak een declaratieoverzicht
Mag je je reiskosten ergens declareren? Je selecteert in de app de maand en de ritten die je in je overzicht wilt krijgen. De app doet de rest. Je krijgt je overzicht als pdf in je mailbox. Of deel het vanuit de app.
 
• Meer passen aan de app toevoegen
Reis je met verschillende passen? Goed nieuws! Je kunt nu meer dan 1 pas aan de app toevoegen. En geef ze direct ook een eigen kleur of naam.
 
• Leeftijdskorting aan je pas toevoegen
Heb je recht op leeftijdskorting? Dan kun je deze korting van 34% nu in de app aan je betaalpas toevoegen. Dit doe je door je naam, geboortedatum en foto door te geven.
 
 
Natuurlijk blijven we de app uitbreiden met handige functies. Hou onze website, Instagram of Facebook in de gaten voor het laatste nieuws.
 
Wie is OVpay?
OVpay is een samenwerking van alle ov-vervoerders van Nederland: Arriva, EBS, GVB, HTM, Keolis, NS, Qbuzz, RET en Transdev. Samen met Translink. En alle grote banken van Nederland doen mee.
 
Deze app hoort bij OVpay. Met OVpay check je in en uit met je betaalpas, je creditcard of je mobiel. In plaats van je OV-chipkaart.
 
Privacy
Met OVpay kies jij zelf de manier waarop je in- en uitcheckt. Om dit voor elkaar te krijgen, hebben we soms wat meer informatie van je nodig. We vinden het belangrijk dat je zelf beslist hoe je persoonsgegevens worden gebruikt. En door wie. In onze privacyverklaring (www.ovpay.nl/privacy) staat hoe we omgaan met je persoonsgegevens.

data.description:
**Hızlı ve Kolay Yatırım Yap

Uygulamayı indirerek dakikalar içinde yatırım hesabını açabilir, para yatırıp hemen yatırıma başlayabilirsin.

**Amerikan Borsasından Hisse Al

Yatırım hesabınla NASDAQ ve New York Stock Exchange üzerindeki hisselere ve borsa yatırım fonlarına yatırım yapabilirsin. Apple, Tesla ve Amazon gibi dünyaca ünlü şirketlerin hisse senetlerini dilediğin tutarda tek tıkla alabilirsin.

**Avantajlı Kur Oranları

Midas yatırım hesabına Türk Lirası ya da Amerikan Doları gönderebilirsin. Ayrıca avantajlı kur oranlarıyla dolar alım-satım işlemleri yaparak Amerikan borsalarına ya da Borsa İstanbul'a yatırım yapabilirsin.

**Borsa İstanbul'da Hisse Al-Sat 

Borsa İstanbul'daki Türk Hava Yolları, Aselsan, Tüpraş ve Enka gibi şirketlere yatırım yapabilir; BIMAS, FROTO gibi hisseleri portföyüne ekleyerek temettü alabilirsin.

**Midas SPK Lisanslı, Güvenilir Bir Kurumdur

Tıpkı bankalar gibi Midas da düzenli olarak denetlenen ve belli regülasyonlar çerçevesinde hareket eden bir finans uygulamasıdır.

*SIPC Hesap Güvencesi

Yatırım hesabına $500.000’a kadar SIPC hesap güvencesi Türkiye'de ilk defa Midas yatırım hesabında.

**Halka Arza Katılım Midas'ta!

Midas yatırım hesabınla borsada satış yöntemiyle halka arzlara katılabilirsin. Şirketin ismini veya borsa kodunu yazıp talep ettiğin hisse adedini girerek, yani birkaç adımda kolayca borsadan satış yöntemiyle halka arzlara katılım sağlayabilirsin.

**Yatırım Fonları Midas'ta!**

Midas yatırım hesabınla fon alıp satabilirsin. Tema ve koleksiyonlarla fonları kolayca inceleyebilir, yeni fonlar keşfedebilirsin. Üstelik altın, gümüş gibi emtialara yatırım yapabileceğin fonlar da Midas'ta seni bekliyor. TEFAS fonlarında komisyon ödemediğin gibi hesap işletim ya da saklama ücreti vb. masraflarla da uğraşmazsın.

**Hisse Senedi Al

Kullanıcı dostu arayüzü ile Midas'ta hisse al-sat işlemleri çok kolay! Midas uygulamasındaki Borsa İstanbul ve Amerikan borsalarına dair güncel içerikleri ve uzman hisse listelerini takip ederek yatırımlarına kolayca yön verebilirsin.

**Parça Hisse ile Dilediğin Tutarda Hisse Al

Amerikan borsalarında hisse fiyatı ne olursa olsun, dilediğin hisseyi bütçene uygun tutarla almanı sağlayan "Parça Hisse" özelliği Türkiye'de ilk defa Midas'ta.

**Ücretsiz Canlı Borsa Verisi Midas'ta!

İlgilendiğin hisseleri Takip Listene ekleyip hisse fiyatlarını ANLIK olarak izleyebilirsin.

**Midas'ta Altın Alım-Satım Fırsatı

Darphane tarafından halka arz edilen Altın Sertifikası Midas'ta! Midas yatırım hesabınla; vergi ödemeden, dilediğin zaman nakde veya fiziksel altına da dönüştürebileceğin Altın Sertifikası alabilirsin.

*Dünya Piyasaları Cebinde

Türk ve Amerikan borsalarına dair güncel haberler, analizler; piyasalara yön veren finans ve ekonomi haberleri ile borsa gündemini takip etmek çok kolay.

"Piyasalar" sayfasından BIST 100 ve BIST 30 gibi BIST endekslerinin yanı sıra S&P 500 ve Nasdaq gibi Amerikan borsalarındaki endeksleri de takip edebilirsin.

**Gizli ve Ek Ücret Yok

Diğer aracı kurumlar, periyodik olarak hesap işletim ücreti alırken Midas'ta hesap işletim ücreti ödemene gerek yoktur. Midas ile işlem yapmasan bile yatırımların Midas hesabında durduğu sürece hiçbir ek ücret ödemezsin. Böylece masraf hesaplama yapmana gerek kalmadan yatırımlarına odaklanırsın.

Her türlü öneri ve soru için destek@getmidas.com adresimizden veya getmidas.com ve midasmenkul.com adresinden ulaşabilirsin.

Midas ile Hemen Yatırıma Başla!

Aracılık hizmetleri, yatırım hizmet ve faaliyetleri, Sermaye Piyasası tarafından yetkilendirilen lisanslı Midas Menkul Değerler A.Ş. aracılığıyla sunulmaktadır. Sunulan hizmetlere erişim Midas Finansal Teknolojiler A.Ş. tarafından sağlanan Midas mobil uygulaması üzerinden sağlanmaktadır.

Locket is a widget that shows live photos from your best friends, right to your Home Screen. You and your best friends will see new pictures from each other every time you unlock your phone. It’s a little glimpse of what everyone’s up to throughout the day.
 
HOW IT WORKS
1. Add the Locket widget to your Home Screen
2. When a friend sends you a photo, it instantly appears on your Locket widget!
3. To share a pic back, tap into the widget, take a pic with the camera, and then hit send! It appears right on your friends’ Home Screens
 
FOR YOUR CLOSE FRIENDS
• To keep things friendly, you can only have 20 friends on the app.
• On Locket, there’s no worrying about follower count, just add your best friends and family and live in the moment.
• With Locket, you’re able to be real and share photos to the people that matter.
 
REACT TO FRIENDS' PHOTOS
• Send a Locket reaction to your friends to let them know you saw their image.
• They’ll get a notification and you’ll love watching the emojis rain down on your photo.
• We don’t count or track the reactions, so you can be real and authentic without worrying about likes and filters like other platforms.
 
BUILD A HISTORY OF YOUR LOCKETS
• As you and friends snap Lockets, you’ll build up a history of all images sent.
• Share them out as photos or use our video recap feature to stitch together the memories of you and your friends, capturing those “love it” moments.
• Locket will also make you a recap video at the end of every month with all of the photos you've shared.
 
ADD LOCKETS FOR YOUR BESTIES AND CRUSHES
• Decorate your home screen with more photos and images dedicated to your crush or your bestie
• Add the “Crush” or “Best Friend” picture widget, and see photos only from that person. Plus, you can send images just to that person too!

Plus, users love our camera (so you’ll love the photos!) - @sonnielove3 on Twitter even said, “It’s sum about that locket camera”
 
Download the free app! We’re keeping Locket free so you can send photos to the people that matter (friends, family, bestie, etc.). With Locket, your phone will feel like it’s bringing you closer to your best friends.
 
Please write to us at team@locketcamera.com. Thanks for having Locket on your Home Screen!

data.releaseNotes: Kalshi is America's #1 prediction market platform. Get in on the action by trading on real-world events like elections, sports, crypto, and weather. This update includes bug fixes and performance upgrades.
data.description:
Kalshi is the largest legal and federally regulated prediction market app in the U.S. where you can make money by predicting real-world events, including the Pro Football and Pro Basketball season. Trade real outcomes in a federally regulated prediction market. Perfect for sports trading, event trading, forecasting, futures-style markets, and real-world predictions.

It’s like trading stocks — but instead, you trade on events you understand. Predict whether an event will happen or not, and earn money if you’re right.
Join 10M+ users trading thousands of prediction markets across finance, weather, culture, sports, and more. Make money 24/7 on fast, simple event markets.

FINANCIAL MARKETS
Daily S&P 500, Nasdaq 100, WTI oil

ECONOMIC MARKETS
Fed interest rates, Inflation (CPI), GDP, Recession, Gas prices, Mortgage rates

CLIMATE MARKETS
Hurricane strength, Daily city temperatures, Tornado numbers

CULTURE MARKETS
Billboard 100, Oscars, Grammys, Emmys, #1 Hits

HOW KALSHI WORKS
Kalshi is the largest federally regulated prediction exchange where you buy and sell contracts based on event outcomes. Example: NASA announces a manned mission to the moon. Contract prices reflect trader probability estimates. If you think the event will happen, you buy contracts. Contracts cost between 1¢ and 99¢ and can be sold anytime. At market close, each correct contract is worth $1.

TRADE SPORTS
Love day trading? Love sports?
Kalshi lets you trade on real sports outcomes across football, baseball, basketball, golf, MMA, tennis, and more.
Will Baltimore beat Philly?
Will the total score go over 45?
Trade pro and college sports with highly liquid prediction markets. Experience live sports trading with unmatched market activity.

HOW IS KALSHI REGULATED?
Kalshi is federally regulated as a Designated Contract Market (DCM) by the Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC). Kalshi’s affiliate, Kalshi Klear LLC, is a CFTC-regulated clearinghouse that holds member funds and clears trades.

TRADE YOUR CONVICTIONS
Find prediction markets that match your views. If you think a recession is coming, trade recession and S&P markets. Put your money behind your forecasts.

REDUCE FINANCIAL RISK
Hedge against events that could impact your finances. If you hold stocks, trade Fed and inflation markets to help protect your portfolio.

KALSHI VS. STOCKS
Event contracts are direct. You trade the outcome of an event, not the future stock price of a company. Profits are not tied to company performance. No pattern day trading restrictions. Trade as much or as little as you want, anytime. In stock trading, you can be right and still lose money due to market sentiment or news. Prediction markets remove that layer.

KALSHI VS. OPTIONS
Event contracts are simpler. Options pricing depends on multiple complex factors. Kalshi contracts reflect straightforward event probabilities. No time decay. If the event odds stay the same, contract value stays stable.

HOW MUCH MONEY DO I NEED TO START?
Open and maintain a Kalshi account for free. Prediction markets require less capital than traditional trading, making it easier to diversify without risking large amounts.

ADVANCED TOOLS & API ACCESS
Build trading algorithms in Python with starter code and a dedicated package. Start in minutes with documentation. Backtest strategies using historical data. Access open-source tools from the Kalshi developer community.

WHO KALSHI IS FOR
Sports fans who want to trade real game outcomes
Traders looking for federally regulated prediction markets
Investors hedging financial risk with event contracts
Forecasters who want to profit from real-world predictions
Developers building automated trading strategies

Say more with Threads — Instagram’s text-based conversation app.

Threads is where communities come together to discuss everything from the topics you care about today to what’ll be trending tomorrow. Whatever it is you’re interested in, you can follow and connect directly with your favorite creators and others who love the same things — or build a loyal following of your own to share your ideas, opinions and creativity with the world!

A few things you can do on Threads…

■ Access your Instagram followers
Your Instagram username and verification badge are reserved for you. Automatically follow the same accounts you follow on Instagram in a few taps, and discover new accounts too.

■ Share your point of view
Spin up a new thread to express what's on your mind. This is your space to be yourself, and you control who can reply.

■ Connect with friends and your favorite creators
Jump to the replies to get in on the action and react to commentary, humor and insight from the creators you know and love. Find your community and connect with people who care about whatever it is you’re interested in.

■ Control the conversation
Customize your settings and use controls to manage who can see your content, reply to your threads, or mention you. Accounts you’ve blocked will carry over from Instagram, and we’re enforcing the same Community Guidelines to help ensure everyone interacts safely and authentically. 

■ Find ideas and inspiration
From TV recommendations to career advice, get answers to your questions or learn something new from crowd-sourced conversations, thought leaders and industry experts.

■ Never miss a moment
Stay on top of the latest trends and live events. Whether it’s about new music, movie premieres, sports, games, TV shows, fashion, or the latest product releases, find discussions and receive notifications any time your favorite profiles start a new thread.

■ Leap into the fediverse
Threads is part of the fediverse, a global, open, social network of independent servers operated by third parties around the world. Servers share information with each other to enable people to connect and discover new things across the fediverse.

Studley AI – The AI Study Tool That Gets You Straight A’s

Forget boring flashcards and endless Google searches. Studley AI is your personal AI homework helper, AI note taker, and AI tutor. Built for students who want insane results. Whether you’re trying to keep a 4.0 GPA or just trying to pass with less stress, Studley is the smartest way to study.

Turn anything into a Study Set:
Upload your lecture slides, textbook chapter, YouTube video, PDF, or even an article link, and Studley instantly turns it into a fully editable Study Set. 

A Study Set can include:

- Flashcards (perfect for memorization)
- Multiple-choice quizzes (test your recall fast)
- Fill-in-the-blanks (strengthen active recall)
- Written tests (practice full answers)
- Tutor mode (AI explains concepts like a personal teacher)

Every question is automatically tagged (e.g., unfamiliar, learning, familiar, mastered) so you can track progress in real time. You’ll literally see your weak spots disappear as you move questions into higher mastery levels.

Progress tracking that actually works:


Our system uses Active Recall and spaced repetition to make sure you remember what you learn long term. No more rereading notes 10 times. Studley forces your brain to work with memory science, not against it. You’ll walk into every exam feeling like you’ve already taken it.

The Solve Tab – Instant Answers, Step-by-Step:


Got a tough homework problem or confusing question? Just take a pic in the Solve tab, and Studley’s AI gives you step-by-step explanations. Not just the answer. This is your 24/7 tutor that never judges you for asking “dumb” questions.

Why Studley AI beats Quizlet (and everything else):

- Smarter AI – You’re not stuck with generic flashcards; every question is made from your content.
- Tagging system – Quizlet can’t show you exactly which questions you’ve mastered vs. which still trip you up. Studley can.
- Fully editable – Change, add, or delete anything. Make it 100% your style.
- All-in-one – No switching between apps for notes, practice tests, and tutors. It’s all here.
- Built for the students who actually want to win.

Studley is powered by proven study methods like:

- Active Recall – Forces you to retrieve info from memory, which strengthens retention.
- Spaced Repetition – Keeps reviewing just before you forget, so it sticks forever.
- Bloom’s Taxonomy – Helps you move beyond memorization into deeper understanding.
- Feynman Technique – Makes sure you can explain concepts clearly, not just repeat them.

How students are using Studley to get a 4.0 GPA:

- Prepping for finals in half the time by turning whole courses into Study Sets.
- Using the tagging system to focus only on “unfamiliar” questions until they’re mastered.
- Swapping Quizlet for Studley to have AI generate better practice questions from any content.
- Getting AI tutoring on hard topics without paying $50/hour.

Why you’ll never go back to old-school studying:

- Fast – Turn any material into a Study Set in seconds.
- Personalized – Tags + progress tracking keep you working only on what matters.
- Affordable – All the features of a private tutor, without the price.
- Proven – Based on real memory science, not gimmicks.

Free to try. Access is limited on the free plan. Upgrade to get unlimited Study Sets and Solve Tab usage.

De meest populaire series en films van HBO, DC Universe, Discovery en meer.

Met HBO Max krijg je:

Functies:
• Geniet van je favoriete series en films, thuis en onderweg. HBO Max is beschikbaar op bepaalde tv's, webbrowsers, mobiele apparaten, tablets en gameconsoles. (Beschikbaarheid voor apparaten kan verschillen per regio en abonnement.)
• Zoek eenvoudig op HBO naar films, series, genres en merken.
• Download je favoriete series en films om onderweg te kijken met geselecteerde abonnementen. (Downloadlimieten verschillen per abonnement.)
• Maak gepersonaliseerde profielen voor het hele gezin met aanpasbare classificaties en beveiligingsopties voor profielpincodes.
• Kijk op je favoriete apparaat verder naar afleveringen en films.
• Met Mijn lijst heb je op één plek toegang tot al je favoriete content.
• Kijk tegelijkertijd op meerdere apparaten. (Limieten verschillen per abonnement.)
• Stream video van hoge kwaliteit met een resolutie van 4K en surround-geluid, waaronder Dolby Atmos-opties die beschikbaar zijn voor geselecteerde abonnementen.

De beschikbaarheid van titels en functies op HBO Max kan per regio variëren. Sommige titels en functies die hierboven zijn weergegeven, zijn mogelijk niet beschikbaar in jouw land. De beschikbaarheid van talen verschilt per land. 

Je abonnement wordt automatisch verlengd tegen de dan geldende prijs van je abonnement, tenzij 'automatisch verlengen' ten minste 24 uur voor verlenging wordt uitgeschakeld. Bij verlenging wordt binnen 24 uur voor het einde van de huidige abonnementsperiode automatisch hetzelfde bedrag in rekening gebracht bij je App Store-account. Je kunt je abonnement beheren of opzeggen via de App Store-app of door op je Apple-device te gaan naar: Instellingen > Abonnementen. 

De doeleinden die worden weergegeven in het privacy-label van de app kunnen variëren op basis van functies of services die mogelijk niet beschikbaar zijn in alle regio's. HBO Max is alleen beschikbaar in bepaalde regio's. 

Gebruiksvoorwaarden: https://hbomax.com/terms-of-use

data.description:
De officiële Museumkaart-app: je digitale toegang tot meer dan 500 Nederlandse musea. Bekijk tentoonstellingen, activiteiten en zet je Museumkaart om naar een digitale pas. Loop voortaan zonder wachten alle aangesloten musea binnen.

Hoe werkt het?
Koop een Museumkaart of geef er een cadeau. Heb je al een Museumkaart? In de app kun je jouw Museumkaart eenvoudig omzetten naar een digitale Museumkaart. Zo heb je altijd je Museumkaart bij de hand. Ook die van je partner of kind kun je in de app zetten.
Bij het museum toon je je persoonlijke digitale Museumkaart in de app.
Heb je een cadeaukaart gekregen of een fysieke tijdelijke kaart in het museum gekocht? Ook die zet je in de app eenvoudig om naar een digitale Museumkaart die meteen geldig is. Ter beveiliging krijg je via jouw e-mailadres je toegangscode. Nooit meer wachten bij de brievenbus tot je plastic pas binnenkomt, altijd je Museumkaart op zak. 

Wat vind je in de app
Wil je weten welk museum er bij jou in de buurt is? Wil je ontdekken welke tentoonstellingen er in jouw favoriete museum zijn? Je vindt het allemaal eenvoudig in de app. Ook het antwoord op de meest gestelde vragen vind je hier. En kom je er echt niet uit dan is een mailtje naar de klantenservice zo geregeld.  

Museumkaart cadeau. Samen naar het museum is nog leuker. Geef iemand een Museumkaart cadeau. Makkelijk te bestellen via de app.

Museumkaart kopen, verlengen of registreren, musea bezoeken, weten waar de spannendste, leukste, liefste en lekkerste musea zijn. Ook zonder Museumkaart is de Museumkaart-app dé toegang tot de Nederlandse museumwereld.

Veel plezier in het museum!

data.description:
Use the UK ETA app to apply for an electronic travel authorisation (ETA) to come to the UK.

Who can apply

Find out if you need an ETA to travel to the UK at: https://www.gov.uk/electronic-travel-authorisation. 

How to apply on the UK ETA app
1. Take a photo of your passport.
2. Scan the chip in your passport.
3. Scan your face.
4. Take a photo of yourself.
5. Answer some questions about yourself.
6. Pay for your application.

It should only take 10 minutes to apply.

You do not need to enter your travel details.

Before you start

To apply you will need:

• an iPhone 8 or newer with IOS 16 or later
• the passport you will use to travel to the UK
• a credit card, debit card or Apple Pay
• access to your emails

If you're applying for someone else they must be with you. If they are not, you should apply online at: https://www.gov.uk/electronic-travel-authorisation.

If you need to travel soon
You must apply for an ETA before you travel to the UK. You can travel to the UK while waiting for a decision. 

After you apply
You'll usually get a decision within 3 working days, but you may get a quicker decision. Occasionally, it may take longer than 3 working days. 

If your ETA is approved, we'll link this to the passport you applied with. You must use this passport to travel to the UK. 

Privacy and security

The app is safe and secure. No information is stored on the app or your phone after you close it. You can delete the app after you have completed your application.

For information on staying safe online visit the UK Cyber Aware website: https://www.ncsc.gov.uk/cyberaware/home

Accessibility
You can read our accessibility statement at: https://confirm-your-identity.homeoffice.gov.uk/register/eta-app-accessibility

Wie is de imposter onder je vrienden?
Imposter is het ultieme partyspel vol bluffen, raden en sociale deductie. Pak 3-5 vrienden erbij, ga rond één apparaat zitten en ontdek wie er liegt.

Hoe speel je:
1- Alle spelers zien hetzelfde geheime woord—behalve één.
2- De imposter ziet alleen het woord "Imposter."
3- Om de beurt zegt elke speler een woord dat gerelateerd is aan het geheime woord.
4- De imposter moet doen alsof en proberen erbij te horen zonder het woord te kennen.
5- Blijf woorden geven en praten tot iemand denkt dat ze het doorhebben.

Leuk, snel en vol achterdocht—perfect voor spelletjesavonden, roadtrips of gewoon chillen met vrienden.

Functies:
- Speel lokaal met 3 tot 15 vrienden
- 10+ categorieën zoals eten, films, banen en meer
- 500+ unieke woorden en groeiend
- Geen accounts, geen setup—gewoon beginnen
- Geweldig voor alle leeftijden—kinderen, tieners en volwassenen

Gemaakt voor lachen, bluffen en epische "aha!" momenten

Download nu en start je volgende Imposter showdown!

data.description:
Als deelnemer van de VriendenLoterij heeft u met de VriendenLoterij App direct toegang tot heel veel voordeel. Uw persoonlijke VIP-KAART(EN) heeft u digitaal binnen handbereik en u ziet direct of u gewonnen heeft. Vanuit de app kunt u ook gemakkelijk meedoen aan extra winacties.

Met de VriendenLoterij App zoekt u gemakkelijk binnen het kortingsaanbod aan vele uitjes. Ontdek wat er bij u in de buurt te beleven valt en sla uw keuzes op onder favorieten voor bijvoorbeeld het perfecte familie-uitje.

Met de VIP-KAART heeft u als deelnemer van de VriendenLoterij gratis toegang bij ruim 150 musea in Nederland en tot 50% korting op vele uitjes: van een voorstelling bij een theater, een filmavond in de bioscoop tot een bezoek aan een dierenpark, pretpark of kasteel. Ook maakt u kans op unieke aanbiedingen zoals toegang tot speciale evenementen en musicals.

Nog geen deelnemer? Speel dan mee, maak een Mijn VriendenLoterij-account aan en vind uw VIP-KAART, al het voordeel en uw lot(en) direct in uw app. Kijk op vriendenloterij.nl/meespelen

data.description:
ParkBee – Slimmer en eenvoudiger parkeren voor een betere prijs

Ben je het zat om eindeloos rond te rijden of veel te betalen voor straatparkeren?
Met ParkBee reserveer je in een paar tikken een veilige parkeerplek van de straat. Een slimmere en vaak goedkopere manier om te parkeren.

Of je nu onderweg bent naar werk, een afspraak of een avondje uit, met ParkBee vind en reserveer je eenvoudig een plek dichtbij je bestemming.

Zo werkt het, in 3 eenvoudige stappen:
1. Zoek een beschikbare parkeerplek in de buurt van je locatie of bestemming
2. Reserveer & betaal veilig in de app
3. Open de app bij aankomst om je sessie te starten en te parkeren.

Waarom kiezen voor ParkBee?
• Toegang tot parkeerplekken die je normaal niet ziet
• Reserveer vooraf en voorkom stress en zoeken op het laatste moment
• Ideaal voor woon-werkverkeer, afspraken of een dagje uit

Handige functies:
• Reserveer eenvoudig je favoriete locaties opnieuw
• Bekijk je parkeergeschiedenis en aankomende reserveringen
• Gebruik locatieservices om snel een parkeerplek in de buurt te vinden

Download nu de ParkBee-app en parkeer slimmer.
Duizenden bestuurders gingen je voor, bespaar tijd en geld met ParkBee.
